        Product Description

        POPIO High Definition Tempered Glass Screen Protector for iPhone 15 / 16

        • POPIO Tempered Glass is crafted to provide exceptional screen protection and high clarity for your 15 / 16 smartphone. Made with advanced toughened glass technology, it helps shield your screen from daily scratches, scuffs, and minor impacts while maintaining a smooth touch experience and crystal-clear visibility.

        • Designed with a precision-cut edge-to-edge layout, it offers full-screen coverage with a sleek black frame that complements your device perfectly. The case-friendly fit ensures secure installation without disturbing your phone cover.

        • The anti-fingerprint and smudge-resistant coating keeps your screen clean and responsive, providing a clear view for gaming, watching videos, or browsing.

        • Installation is simple with the included installation kit and cleaning kit, allowing for a bubble-free and accurate fit every time. POPIO brings reliable protection, smooth usability, and lasting clarity keeping your screen safe and looking fresh.

        Frequently Asked Questions:

        1. The flexibility of the Glass Screen Protector is just the same as the plastic material, Is it made of tempered glass or plastic?

        This screen protector is a real tempered glass. The plastic like flexibility is the exact reason why we call it tempered glass screen protector. Tempered or toughened glass is a type of safety glass processed by controlled thermal or chemical treatments to increase its strength compared with normal glass.

        2. Does it come with a cleaning wipe to use prior to placing on the phone?

        Yes, the package includes: 3 x Guide Stickers, 1 x Wet Wipe & 1 x Microfiber Cloth, 1 x Dust Absorber

        3. Does the screen protector cover the whole screen? Why is it slightly smaller than my phone's screen?

        Due to the rounded edge of the phone and to enhance compatibility with most cases, the tempered glass covers most of the screen. It is effective for preventing bubbling and peeling at the edges.

        4. How can I remove bubbles?

        Before placing the screen protector, please first clean the screen by using kits in the package. If there are bubbles, please try to press the bubble by using your finger with a little force, and try to use a ruler or a credit card to help you with the problem, but a thin cloth pad is needed on the surface of the screen to avoid scratches the protector.

        5. Is it compatible with other cases?

        Yes. It has case friendly design. It works with most cases. There is a small gap from the edge of screen protector to phones edge to ensure it is compatible with most case. Only those covers with rigid & heavy borders , this glass is not compatible.

        6. Is this Glass compatible with iPhone 15 Plus or iPhone 16 Plus ?

        Strictly No, This Glass is NOT Compatible With iPhone 15 Plus or iPhone 16 Plus .
